<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PC Shop - Componentes</title>
    <style>
        /* Estilos para el spinner de carga */
        #loadingSpinner {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        .imagen-componente {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .spinner {
            border: 8px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 8px solid #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="loadingSpinner">
        <div class="spinner"></div>
    </div>

    <header>
        <h1>Componentes en PC Shop</h1>
        <p>Encuentra los mejores componentes para ensamblar o actualizar tu computadora.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Nuestros Componentes</h2>
        <div>
            <figure>
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQEXTWDqQx9cS2uAhol_yIeYO1PT56RsIS9MA&s" class="imagen-componente">
                <figcaption>Procesador Intel Core i9</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
                <img src="https://i0.wp.com/rayotec.pe/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/40608.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1" class="imagen-componente">
                <figcaption>Tarjeta gr√°fica NVIDIA RTX</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <figure>
                <img src="https://http2.mlstatic.com/D_NQ_NP_908774-MPE70482462792_072023-O.webp" class="imagen-componente">
                <figcaption>Memoria RAM Corsair 16GB</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener("load", function() {
            document.getElementById("loadingSpinner").style.display = "none";
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
